channel.title: Need gs mini help ! please read!
channel.description: Hello as i want to improve my server and add a proper gs mini like runescape for example have General Graador drop god sword at the end, but as i add the id's in and compile, run server and log in the NPC's that i wanted are totally different i dont know whats happend, its like i cant seem to have silab NPC's or summin lol whats up ? please someone help and explain please thankyou!!

item.title: Need gs mini help ! please read!
item.dc:creator: @M_i_K_e1 M,i,K,e_
item.description:
@M_i_K_e1 wrote:

[quote=“keepitreal, post:1, topic:200395”]Hello as i want to improve my server and add a proper gs mini like runescape for example have General Graador drop god sword at the end, but as i add the id’s in and compile, run server and log in the NPC’s that i wanted are totally different i dont know whats happend, its like i cant seem to have silab NPC’s or summin lol
whats up ?
please someone help and explain please thankyou!![/quote]

Seriously? Okay so you take an npc model put it in your client’s model folder then 'add model ’ then you call it an NPC, such as an item ‘Silab’ = no no, PLAIN REGULAR ‘ITEM’ ‘NPC’ ‘OBJECT’

We also accept ‘RuneScape / Jagex’ item/npc/object.
